<div id="aboutSection">
    <h2 class="hidden">About Me Section</h2>

        <h2 class="hidden">About Me Image</h2>
        <img src="images/self_pic_1.png" id="aboutImg" alt="Michael Prior self Picture">

    <div id="aboutLeft">
        <div id="aboutCopy">
            <h2 class="hidden">About Me Copy</h2>
            <p>Hello my name is Michael Prior, I am a designer and artist from the London Ontario area. I am a student at Fanshawe College, in the Interactive Media Design program. Once graduated, I plan to continue learning new and exciting ways of developing interesting content.</p>
            <p>Thanks to my mother, I developed a love for art and design from a young age while attending the local YMCA art camps that she ran. I spent most of my life sketching and drawing comic type characters, and redesgining Picso and Myspace pages (usually quite terribly) to share my interests with my close friends. Eventually, I stated to learn about all the ways you can create fun and interesting content digitally.</p>
            <p>My goal is always to continuously create visually stimulating content for a variety of clients, while making the interaction between the client and the end user seemless and easy.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{{!-- PORTFOLIO gallery SECTION --}}
<div id="portTitleCon">
    <img src="images/port_title.png" id="portTitle" class="title" alt="My Portfolio Title">
</div>
<section id="portfolioSection" class="section">
    <h2 class="hidden">My Portfolio</h2>
    <div class="faveThings">
        <!-- loop through db and put the info on the page -->
        {{#each thing}} <!-- A for each loop -->
        <div class="thing">
            {{!-- title from db --}}
            <h2>{{Title}}</h2>
            {{!-- img from db --}}
            <img src="images/{{Image}}" alt="Video Game Cover" class="thingImage">
            {{!-- title from db --}}
            <h3>{{Role}}</h3>
            <a class="link" href="{{Link}}">{{Link}}</a>
            <!-- Place Piece info here -->
            <p class="info" id="info{{ID}}"></p>
            {{!-- See more button --}}
            <a href="{{ID}}" class="seeMore" id="seeMore{{ID}}">More Info</a>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
</section>


